  <title>Past Flyers</title>

  <para>
    Here are a collection of sample flyers which we have used to
    advertise speakers for a variety of events. Each flyer contains a
    short bit of text describing the event and all of the relevant
    information needed to attend. Make sure to include links to
    website post and/or QR codes <footnote><para><link
    xl:href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QR_code">Read about QR Codes
    on Wikipedia</link></para></footnote> <footnote><para><link
    xl:href="http://qrcode.kaywa.com/">QR Code
    Generator</link></para></footnote> so that students can just use
    their phone to bookmark the event quickly.
  </para>
  
